column13:
Playlists are created with the following structure:

1. Formulators are divided into their respective lines for the day based on the schedule.
2. SpotiFire searches for each artist on Spotify. Spelling must be correct!
3. For each artist, it retrieves the top ten tracks of the artist, then selects a random track from each of the three most related artists.
4. For each formulator, 30 of their tracks are selected and added to their lines playlist.
5. Finally, they are created as public playlists under my account: https://open.spotify.com/user/22ohoemhot7m75uv2ol5jgfga?si=89e3310df9724069

Explicit tracks are filtered out so choose your artists wisely☠️
